1130
01:34:33,270 --> 01:34:34,310
Firdaus teacher?

1131
01:34:40,270 --> 01:34:41,270
Hi.

1132
01:34:44,940 --> 01:34:45,940
May I come in?

1133
01:34:45,980 --> 01:34:46,980
