1177
01:38:11,650 --> 01:38:17,900
When we'll get together.

1178
01:38:18,940 --> 01:38:26,650
Heaven and earth will come alive.

1179
01:38:26,810 --> 01:38:32,940
When we'll get together.

1180
01:38:34,230 --> 01:38:41,230
